Name: Blink Dagger
Description:
Active: Blink

Teleport to a target point up to %blink_range% units away.

Blink Dagger cannot be used for %blink_damage_cooldown% seconds after taking damage from an enemy hero or Roshan.

Name: Overwhelming Blink
Description:
Active: Overwhelming Blink

Teleport to a target point up to %blink_range% units away.

After teleportation, all enemies in a %radius% AoE take damage equal to %damage_base% + %damage_pct_instant%% of your strength and an additional %damage_pct_over_time%% over time, and have %movement_slow%% movement speed slow and %attack_slow% attack speed slow for %duration% seconds.

Overwhelming Blink cannot be used for %blink_damage_cooldown% seconds after taking damage from an enemy hero or Roshan.

Description:
Active: Swift Blink

Teleport to a target point up to %blink_range% units away.

After teleportation, you gain %bonus_movement%% phased movement speed and +%bonus_agi_active% Agility for %duration% seconds.

Swift Blink cannot be used for %blink_damage_cooldown% seconds after taking damage from an enemy hero or Roshan.

Name: Arcane Blink
Description:
Active: Arcane Blink

Teleport to a target point up to %blink_range% units away.

After teleportation, you restore %heal_amount% health and %mana_amount% mana.

Arcane Blink cannot be used for %blink_damage_cooldown% seconds after taking damage from an enemy hero or Roshan.

Name: Javelin
Description:
Passive: Pierce

Grants each attack a %bonus_chance%% chance to pierce through evasion and deal %bonus_chance_damage% bonus magical damage.

Name: Quelling Blade
Description:

Destroy a target tree.

Increases attack damage against non-hero units by %damage_bonus% for melee heroes, and %damage_bonus_ranged% for ranged.

Name: Faerie Fire
Description:
Use: Imbue

Instantly restores %hp_restore% health.

Name: Infused Raindrops
Description:
Passive: Magical Damage Block

Consumes a charge to block %magic_damage_block% magic damage from damage instances over %min_damage% damage.

Comes with %initial_charges% charges. When the charges are gone, the item disappears.

Name: Wind Lace
Description: Bonuses from multiple Wind Laces do not stack.

Name: Stout Shield
Description:
Passive: Damage Block

Grants a %block_chance%% chance to block %damage_block_melee% damage from incoming attacks on melee heroes, and %damage_block_ranged% damage on ranged.

Name: Moon Shard
Description:
Use: Consume

Consume the Moon Shard to permanently gain %consumed_bonus% attack speed and %consumed_bonus_night_vision% bonus night vision. Max 1 use.

Passive: Shade Sight

Grants bonus night vision.

Name: Iron Branch
Description:
Use: Plant Tree

Targets the ground to plant a happy little tree that lasts for %tree_duration% seconds.

Name: Morbid Mask
Description:
Passive: Lifesteal

Heals the attacker for a percentage of attack damage dealt. Lifesteal from creeps is reduced by %creep_lifesteal_reduction_pct%%.

Name: Voodoo Mask
Description:
Passive: Spell Lifesteal

Spell damage dealt to enemy heroes is returned to the caster as health, regardless of spell damage type.

Lifesteal reduced against creeps.

Name: Boots of Speed
Description: Movement speed bonuses from multiple pairs of boots do not stack.

Name: Gem of True Sight
Description:
Active: Reveal

Gives True Sight over a %active_radius% radius revealing wards and units even in Fog of War.

Passive: True Sight

Grants the ability to see invisible units and wards to any allied vision within %radius% range of its carrier.

Passive: Everlasting

Dropped on death, and cannot be destroyed.

Name: Cheese
Description:
Use: Fondue

Instantly restores %health_restore% health and %mana_restore% mana.

Name: Magic Stick
Description:

Instantly restores %restore_per_charge% health and mana per charge stored.

Max %max_charges% charges. Gains a charge whenever a visible enemy within %charge_radius% range uses an ability.

Name: Magic Wand
Description:
Active: Energy Charge

Instantly restores %restore_per_charge% health and mana per charge stored.

Max %max_charges% charges. Gains a charge whenever a visible enemy within %charge_radius% range uses an ability.

Name: Ghost Scepter

You enter ghost form for %duration% seconds, becoming immune to physical damage, but are unable to attack and %extra_spell_damage_percent%% more vulnerable to magic damage.

Name: Clarity
Description:

Use: Eat Mango

Description:
Use: Eat Lotus

Instantly restores %replenish_amount% health and mana.

Name: Blood Grenade
Description:
Use: Throw Grenade

Throw a grenade at the target area. Enemies in the area will take %impact_damage% damage on impact, and be slowed by %movespeed_slow%% and take %damage_over_time% damage every %tick_rate%s for %debuff_duration% seconds. Radius %radius%.

Name: Block of Cheese
Description:
Use: Scrumptious

Try me!

Name: Healing Salve
Description:
Use: Salve

Grants %health_regen% health regeneration to the target for %buff_duration% seconds.

If the unit is attacked by an enemy hero or Roshan, the effect is lost.

Heals for half the amount when cast on an ally.

Name: Dust of Appearance
Description:
Use: Reveal

For %duration% seconds, creates an area that reveals and slows invisible heroes by %movespeed%% in a %radius% radius where the caster was standing. Invisible units revealed by dust take %damage% damage.

The debuff effect on enemies lingers for %linger_duration%s after leaving the area of effect.

Name: Bottle
Description:
Active: Regenerate

Consumes a charge to restore %health_restore% health and %mana_restore% mana over %restore_time% seconds. If the hero is attacked by an enemy hero or Roshan, the effect is lost.

The Bottle automatically refills at the fountain.

Hold Control to use on an allied hero.

Passive: Store Rune

Runes can be stored in the Bottle for later use by right-clicking them. Unused runes will automatically activate after 90 seconds.

Using a stored rune fully refills the Bottle.

Name: Observer Ward
Description:
Use: Plant

Plants an Observer Ward, an invisible watcher that gives ground vision in a %vision_range_tooltip% radius to your team. Lasts %duration_minutes_tooltip% minutes.

Hold Control to give one Observer Ward to an allied hero.

Name: Sentry Ward
Description:
Use: Plant

Plants a Sentry Ward, an invisible watcher that grants True Sight, the ability to see invisible enemy units and wards, to any existing allied vision within a %true_sight_range% radius.
Lasts %duration_minutes_tooltip% minutes.

Does not grant ground vision.
Hold Control to give one Sentry Ward to an allied hero.

Name: Observer and Sentry Wards
Description:
Use: Plant

Plant the currently active ward. Double-Click to switch the currently active ward.

Name: Tango
Description:
Use: Devour

Consumes a target tree to gain %health_regen% health regeneration for %buff_duration% seconds. Consuming an Ironwood Tree doubles the heal amount.

Comes with %tooltip_charges% charges. Can be used on an allied hero to give them one Tango.

Tree Range: %abilitycastrange%

Name: Tango (Shared)
Description:
Use: Devour

Consumes a target tree to gain %health_regen% health regeneration for %buff_duration% seconds. Consuming an Ironwood Tree doubles the heal amount.

Tree Range: %abilitycastrange%

Name: Animal Courier
Description:
Use: Deploy Courier

Deploys a creature to carry items to and from your team's base.

Name: Flying Courier
Description:
Use: Upgrade Courier

Upgrades your team's Animal Courier to a Flying Courier, granting it swift, unobstructed movement to carry items to and from your team's base.

Requires a deployed Animal Courier.

Name: Town Portal Scroll
Description:
Use: Teleport

After channeling for %tooltip_channel_time% seconds, teleports you to a target friendly building.

Double-click to teleport to your team's base fountain.

Name: Boots of Travel
Description:
Upgrade: Town Portal Scroll

Upgrades your Town Portal Scroll, allowing it to target units, reduces cooldown and does not consume a charge on usage. Movement speed bonuses from multiple pairs of boots do not stack.

Name: Boots of Travel 2
Description:
Upgrade: Town Portal Scroll

Upgrades your Town Portal Scroll, allowing it to target units and heroes, reduces cooldown, channel time and does not consume a charge on usage. Movement speed bonuses from multiple pairs of boots do not stack.

Name: Phase Boots
Description:
Active: Phase

Gives %phase_movement_speed%% increased movement speed on melee heroes, and %phase_movement_speed_range%% on ranged heroes, and lets you move through units and turn more quickly for %phase_duration% seconds. Movement speed bonuses from multiple pairs of boots do not stack.

Name: Power Treads
Description:
Active: Switch Attribute

Switches between +%bonus_stat% Strength, +%bonus_stat% Agility, or +%bonus_stat% Intelligence. Movement speed bonuses from multiple pairs of boots do not stack.

Name: Samurai Tabi
Description:
Active: Switch Attribute

Switches between an additional +%bonus_stat_tooltip% Strength, +%bonus_stat_tooltip% Agility, or +%bonus_stat_tooltip% Intelligence, and provides the bonuses corresponding with that parameter.

Intelligence

Once fully charged, deals %int_damage% to %int_max_targets% random targets in %int_damage_range% range every %int_damage_interval% seconds.

Strength

Once fully charged an attack has a %str_root_chance%% chance to deal %str_bonus_damage% bonus damage and root the target for %str_root_duration% seconds. %str_root_cooldown%s Cooldown.

Agility

Once fully charged, when attacked, the hero has a %agi_counter_chance% to counter-attack a target within their attack range. %agi_counter_cooldown%s Cooldown.

Name: Hermes Sandals
Description:
Active: Greater Phase

When activated, the user cannot be slowed or rooted. Gives %phase_movement_speed%% increased movement speed on melee heroes, and %phase_movement_speed_range%% on ranged heroes, and lets you move through units and turn more quickly for %phase_duration% seconds. Does not dispel roots that are already in place. Movement speed bonuses from multiple pairs of boots do not stack.

Name: Witches Switch
Description:
Toggle: Switch

When active, Increases allied armor, health regeneration and mana regeneration. When Switched, decreases enemy armor, health regeneration and mana regeneration by the same amount.

Name: Lunar Crest
Description:
Active: Glow

When cast on an enemy, doubles incoming magic damage on them up to a threshhold of %barrier_block% magic damage.

Lasts %duration% seconds.

Name: Phylactery
Description:
Passive: Empower Spell

The next Unit Target spell you cast on an enemy deals a separate %bonus_spell_damage% bonus damage to the target, and slows them by %slow%% for %slow_duration%s.

Name: Khanda
Description:
Passive: Empower Spell

The next Unit Target spell you cast on an enemy deals %spell_crit_flat% + %spell_crit_multiplier%% of your attack damage as bonus damage to the target, and slows them by %slow%% for %slow_duration%s.

Passive: Critical Strike

Grants each attack a %crit_chance%% chance to deal %crit_multiplier%% damage.

Name: Hand of Midas
Description:
Active: Transmute

Kills a non-hero target for %bonus_gold% gold and %xp_multiplier%x experience. When used on a neutral creep, guarantees to create a neutral item if available.

Cannot be used on Ancient creeps.

Name: Aetherial Hammer
Description:
Active: Aetherial Hammer

CHANNELED - After a successful channel, summons a meteor that strikes a %impact_radius% AoE, stunning enemies for %stun_duration% seconds and dealing impact damage. Continues to deal damage over time to enemies units and buildings for %burn_duration% seconds. Non-building units are also slowed for %burn_slow%% for the duration of the burn.

Building Impact Damage: %impact_damage_buildings%
Building Over Time Damage: %burn_dps_buildings%

Non-Building Impact Damage: %impact_damage_units%
Non-Building Over Time Damage: %burn_dps_units%

Channel Duration: %max_duration% seconds.
Landing Time: %land_time% seconds.

Passive:Foci

Increases targeted spell and item Area of Effect by %bonus_aoe%.

Name: Witch Blade
Description:
Passive: Witch Blade

Causes your next attack to apply a poison for %slow_duration% seconds, slowing by %slow%% and dealing %int_damage_multiplier%x your intelligence as damage every second. This attack has True Strike.

Name: Poor Man's Shield
Description:
Passive: Damage Block

Gives a 100% chance to block %damage_block_melee% damage from incoming attacks on melee heroes, and %damage_block_ranged% damage on ranged.

Has a %block_chance%% chance to block damage from creeps.

Name: Satchel
Description: Increases XP that you earn by %xp_gain%%.

Name: Mekansm
Description:
Active: Restore

Restores %heal_amount% health to allied units in a %heal_radius% radius.

Passive: Mekansm Aura

Grants %aura_health_regen% health regeneration to allied units in a %aura_radius% radius.

Name: Vladmir's Offering
Description:
Passive: Vladmir's Aura

Grants %lifesteal_aura%% lifesteal, %damage_aura%% bonus damage, %mana_regen_aura% mana regeneration, and %armor_aura% armor to nearby allies. Lifesteal from creeps is reduced by %creep_lifesteal_reduction_pct%%.

Radius: %aura_radius%

Name: Wraith Pact
Description:
Active: Wraith's Reprisal

Summons a movable totem in your location for %abilityduration% seconds that reduces all physical damage of enemies within %pact_aura_radius% radius by %damage_penalty_aura%% and deals %aura_dps% damage per second.

The totem eminates the Vladmir's Aura around it. Totem can be destroyed in 4 hits. Creeps deal half damage to the totem.

Passive: Vladmir's Aura

Grants %lifesteal_aura%% lifesteal, %damage_aura%% bonus damage, %mana_regen_aura% mana regeneration, and %armor_aura% armor to nearby allies. Lifesteal from creeps is reduced by %creep_lifesteal_reduction_pct%%.

Radius: %aura_radius%

Radius: %aura_radius%

Active: Energy Charge

Target an allied unit to instantly restore %restore_per_charge% health and mana per charge stored.

Automatically gains a charge every %AbilityChargeRestoreTime% seconds and whenever a visible enemy within %charge_radius% range uses an ability.

Passive: Holy Blessing

Amplifies heals you provide by %heal_increase%%.

Name: Pipe of Insight
Description:
Active: Barrier

Gives a magic damage barrier that absorbs %barrier_block% damage to all nearby allies. Lasts %barrier_duration% seconds.

Radius: %barrier_radius%

Passive: Insight Aura

Gives allied units %aura_health_regen% health regeneration and %magic_resistance_aura%% magic resistance.

Radius: %aura_radius%

Name: Urn of Shadows
Description:
Active: Soul Release

Provides %soul_heal_amount% health regeneration when cast on allies, and deals %soul_damage_amount% damage per second when cast on enemies.

Lasts %duration% seconds.

Gains charges every time an enemy hero dies within %soul_radius% units. Only the closest Urn to the dying hero will gain a charge.

Name: Headdress
Description:
Passive: Regeneration Aura

Grants %aura_health_regen% health regeneration to allies.

Radius: %aura_radius%

Name: Scythe of Vyse
Description:
Active: Hex

Turns a target unit into a harmless critter for %sheep_duration% seconds. The target has a base movement speed of %sheep_movement_speed% and will be silenced, muted, and disarmed.
Instantly destroys illusions.

Name: Caster Rapier
Description:
Passive: Everlasting

Dropped on death, and cannot be destroyed.

Becomes unusable if picked up by an ally of its owner until it is returned to its owner. It is immediately usable by anybody if an enemy of the owner picks it up and is killed. A dropped Rapier cannot be picked up by a courier.

Name: Orchid Malevolence
Description:
Active: Soul Burn

Silences the target unit for %silence_duration% seconds. At the end of the silence, %silence_damage_percent%% of the damage received while silenced is inflicted as bonus magical damage.

Name: Bloodthorn
Description:
Active: Soul Rend

Silences a target for %silence_duration% seconds. At the end of the silence, an additional %silence_damage_percent%% of all damage taken during the silence will be dealt to the target as magical damage.

All attacks on the silenced target will deal additional damage equal to %proc_damage_heroes% if the attacker is a hero, and %proc_damage_creeps%, if the attacker is a creep, and have True Strike.

Passive: Pierce

Grants each attack a %proc_chance%% chance to pierce through evasion and deal %passive_proc_damage% bonus magical damage.

Name: Echo Sabre
Description:
Passive: Echo Strike

Causes melee attacks to attack twice in quick succession. The double attacks apply a %movement_slow%% movement slow for %slow_duration% seconds on the first strike.

Name: Eul's Scepter of Divinity
Description:
Active: Cyclone

Sweeps a target unit up into a cyclone, making them invulnerable for %cyclone_duration% seconds. Cyclone can only be cast on enemy units or yourself.

Enemy units take %tooltip_drop_damage% magical damage upon landing.
Dispel Type: Basic Dispel

Name: Wind Waker
Description:

Sweeps a target unit up into a cyclone, making them invulnerable for %cyclone_duration% seconds. Cyclone can be cast on yourself, enemy units or allied units.

Enemy units take %tooltip_drop_damage% magical damage upon landing.

Description:

Pushes you and target enemy %enemy_length% units away from each other, and for %range_duration% seconds, allows you to make %max_attacks% attacks against the target without range restrictions and with +%bonus_attack_speed% attack speed.

Can be cast on self or allies to push the target %push_length% units in the direction it is facing.
Enemy Range: %cast_range_enemy%

Passive: Dragon's Reach

Increases attack range of ranged heroes.

Description:

Resets the cooldowns of all your items and abilities. Shares a cooldown with Refresher Shard. This item's cooldown only progresses in your hero's main inventory.

Description:
Passive: Assault Aura

Grants %aura_attack_speed% attack speed and %aura_positive_armor% armor to nearby allied units and structures, and decreases nearby enemy unit and structure armor by %aura_negative_armor%.

Radius: %aura_radius%

Name: Black King Bar
Description:
Active: Avatar

Applies a basic dispel. Grants %magic_resist%% Magic resistance and immunity to pure and reflected damage. For the duration of the effect, any negative effect from enemy spells has no effect.

Duration: %duration%
Dispel Type: Basic Dispel

Name: Aegis of the Immortal
Description:
Passive: Reincarnation

Brings you to life with full health and mana %reincarnate_time% seconds after you die, at the location where you died.

Reincarnation must be used within %disappear_time_minutes_tooltip% minutes or Aegis of the Immortal disappears. If it expires, it will heal you over 5 seconds (dispels on damage).

Name: Shiva's Guard
Description:
Active: Arctic Blast

Emits a freezing wave that causes enemies to take %spell_amp%% more damage from spells for %resist_debuff_duration% seconds, deals %blast_damage% magical damage and slows their movement by %blast_movement_speed%% for %blast_debuff_duration% seconds. Deals %illusion_multiplier_pct%% damage to illusions.

Radius: %blast_radius%

Reduces the attack speed of all enemies by %aura_attack_speed% and all heals, regeneration and lifesteal by %hp_regen_degen_aura%%.

Description:
Passive: Spellblock

Blocks most targeted spells once every %block_cooldown% seconds.

Active: Transfer Spellblock

Temporarily removes Spellblock from the item's owner and transfers it to an allied unit for %block_cooldown% seconds.

Name: Lotus Orb
Description:
Active: Echo Shell

Applies a shield to the target unit for %active_duration% seconds which re-casts most targeted spells back to their caster.

The shielded unit will still take damage from the spell.

Passive: Combo Breaker

When you take damage and your health falls below %health_threshold_pct%%, a strong dispel is applied and you gain a %buff_duration% second buff that provides +%status_resistance%% Status Resistance and causes all damage you deal and are dealt to be reduced to zero. Only triggers on player based damage. Cooldown increases every time it triggers.

Dispel Type: Strong Dispel

Description:
Active: Soul Release

When used against enemies, it reduces health by %enemy_hp_drain%% of current health per second, and reduces HP regeneration, healing, lifesteal and spell lifesteal by %hp_regen_reduction_enemy%%. Deals %soul_damage_amount% damage per second.

When used on allies, it provides %soul_heal_amount% health regeneration per second.

Lasts %duration% seconds.

Gains charges every time an enemy hero dies within %soul_radius% units or the user dies. Only the closest Spirit Vessel to the dying hero will gain a charge.

Name: Vanguard
Description:
Passive: Damage Block

Grants a %block_chance%% chance to block %block_damage_melee% damage from incoming attacks on melee heroes, and %block_damage_ranged% damage on ranged.

Name: Crimson Guard

Description:
Passive: Death Delay

Survive for an extra %duration% seconds after receiving a killing blow.

Name: Vambrace
Description:
Also provides one of the following, based on the Vambrace's main attribute:
 <font color='#ec3d06'>Strength:</font> +%bonus_magic_resistance%% Magic Resistance 
 <font color='#3ed038'>Agility:</font> +%bonus_attack_speed% Attack Speed 
 <font color='#00d9ec'>Intelligence:</font> +%bonus_spell_amp%% Spell Amp

Name: Horizon
Description:
Active: Blink Strike

Targets a unit to teleport to them. Knocks enemies back %knockback_distance% distance and disables them for %knockback_duration% second.

Name: Fusion Rune
Description:
Use: Consume

Grants the target the bonuses of every Power Rune for %duration% seconds. Each use consumes a charge.

Name: Ocean Heart
Description:
Passive: Water Regen

Provides you with %water_hp_regen% HP regen and %water_mp_regen% mana regen while in the river.

Name: Spark of Courage
Description:
Passive: Courage

Provides %damage% damage when the hero is above %health_pct%% Health, and %armor% armor when they are below that threshold.

Name: Trusty Shovel
Description:
Active: Dig

Channel for 1 second.
Can find a Bounty Rune, a Flask, an Enchanted Mango, or a Kobold. If digging in a river, always digs up a Water Rune.

This item's cooldown only progresses in your hero's Neutral Item slot

Name: Dragon Scale
Description:
Passive: Afterburn

Causes attacks to burn the enemy, dealing %damage_per_sec% damage per second for %duration% seconds. Affects buildings.

Name: Essence Ring
Description:
Active: Life Essence

Increases your current and max health by %health_gain% for %health_gain_duration% seconds.

Name: Clumsy Net
Description:
Active: Ensnare

Ensnares the target enemy and yourself for %duration% seconds.

Name: Enchanted Quiver
Description:
Passive: Certain Strike

Empowers your next attack with %bonus_damage% bonus magical damage and True Strike. Ranged Attackers have +%active_bonus_attack_range% bonus range for the attack.

Name: Ninja Gear
Description:
Active: Solitary Disguise

Casts Smoke of Deceit on yourself only.

Name: Illusionist's Cape
Description:
Active: Create Illusion

Creates an image under your control.

Passive: Illusion Mastery

Increases outgoing damage of all units and illusions controlled by the hero by %attack_damage_aura%%.

Name: Havoc Hammer
Description:
Active: Havoc

Pulls enemies in a %range% range around you, slowing them by %slow%% for %slow_duration% seconds and dealing %nuke_base_dmg% + %nuke_str_dmg%x your str as magical damage.

Name: Magic Lamp
Description:
Passive: Rejuvenate

When the wearer's health falls below %health_threshold%%, they will receive a hard dispel and be healed for %heal% health.

Name: Ballista
Description:
Passive: Knockback

Knocks back enemies %knockback_distance% distance and deals %bonus_damage% pure damage with every attack.

Name: Woodland Striders
Description:
Active: Woodland Stride

Create a path of trees behind you for %active_duration% seconds. Trees last up to %tree_duration% seconds.

Passive: Tree Walking

Removes movement speed limit and allows free pathing through trees. Movement speed bonuses from multiple pairs of boots do not stack.

Name: Book of the Dead
Description:
Active: Greater Demonic Summoning

Summon 2 sets of Level 3 Necronomicon Units that last %summon_duration% seconds. Units have 100% more health and 75% more damage.

Name: Fallen Sky
Description:
Active: Fallen Sky

Transform into a meteor that strikes down at the target area after %land_time% seconds in a %impact_radius% AoE, stunning enemies for %stun_duration% seconds and dealing impact damage. Continues to deal damage every %burn_interval% seconds to enemy units and buildings for %burn_duration% seconds.

Building Impact Damage: %impact_damage_buildings%
Building Over Time Damage: %burn_dps_buildings%

Non-Building Impact Damage: %impact_damage_units%
Non-Building Over Time Damage: %burn_dps_units%

Name: Pirate Hat
Description:
Active: Dig

Channel for 1 second.
Always finds a Bounty Rune!

Name: Dimensional Doorway
Description:
Active

Teleport instantly anywhere on the map.

Name: Ex Machina
Description:
Active: Reset Cooldowns

Reset the cooldown on all items (except Refresher Orb).

Name: Paladin Sword
Description:
Passive: Greater Healing

Amplifies the wearer's Regeneration, Healing, Lifesteal and Spell Lifesteal by %bonus_amp%%.

Name: Minotaur Horn
Description:
Active: Lesser Avatar

Grants Spell Immunity for %duration% seconds.

Name: Orb of Destruction
Description:
Passive: Impeding Corruption

Attacks reduce the target's armor and movement speed. Slow amount varies based on whether the wearer is melee or ranged.

Name: Arcane Ring
Description:
Active: Replenish Mana

Restores %mana_restore% mana to all nearby allies.

Radius: %radius%

Name: Chipped Vest
Description:
Passive

Everytime you are attacked, you return %damage_return_hero% damage to heroes and %damage_return_creep% damage to creeps.

Name: Wizard Glass
Description:
Active

Deals %damage% damage to up to %count% random enemy units within %radius%.

Name: Gloves of Travel
Description: Reduces TP cooldown by %tp_cooldown_reduction% seconds and causes TP scrolls to not be consumed.

Name: Cloak of Flames
Description:
Passive: Immolate

Burns enemy units for %damage% damage per second. Illusions deal %damage_illusions% damage per second.

Radius: %radius%

Name: Trickster Cloak
Description:
Active: Cloak

Causes you to become invisible for %duration% seconds.

Name: Helm of the Gladiator
Description: Upon taking hero damage, you gains %damage% damage, %armor% armor, %movement_speed% for %duration% seconds.

Name: Possessed Mask
Description:
Passive: Lifesteal

Heals the attacker for %lifesteal% HP on each attack.

Name: Star Mace
Description:
Passive: Cleave

Melee heroes deal %cleave_damage_percent%% of attack damage as physical damage in a cone up to %cleave_distance% around the target.

Name: Penta-Edged Sword
Description:
Passive: Maim

Each attack has a %maim_chance%% chance to reduce enemy hero movement speed by %maim_slow_movement%% and attack speed by %maim_slow_attack% for %maim_duration% seconds.

Name: Oakheart
Description:
Active: Rejuvenate

Target an allied hero and restore %heal% health over %duration% seconds.

If the unit is attacked by an enemy hero or Roshan, the effect is lost.

Name: Warhammer
Description:
Active: Warhammer

Deals %damage% damage and reduces the target's armor by %armor_reduction% for %duration% seconds.

Name: Bullwhip
Description:
Active: Whip

Grants %speed%% movement speed when cast on allies, and slows by %speed%% when cast on enemies. Lasts %duration% seconds.

Name: Psychic Headband
Description:
Active: Psychic Push

Pushes the target enemy unit away from you %push_length% distance.

Name: Ceremonial Robe
Description:
Passive: Ceremonial Aura

Lowers enemy Status Resistance by %status_resistance%% and Magic Resistance by %magic_resistance%%.

Radius: %aura_radius%

Name: Quicksilver Amulet
Description:
Passive: Quicksilver

Grants you a bonus %bonus_movement%% movement speed and %bonus_attack% attack speed anytime one of your abilities are on cooldown.

Name: Book of Shadows
Description:
Active: Shadows

Target an enemy, ally or self. Causes the target to become untargetable from enemies to the caster, but also silenced, muted and disarmed for %duration% seconds. Applies a Basic Dispel. Dispel Type: Basic Dispel

Name: Giant's Ring
Description:
Passive: Giant's Foot

Can path over any terrain and deals %pct_str_damage_per_second%% of your strength per second to units you are standing ontop of.

Name: Shadow of Vengeance
Description:
Passive: Vengeance's Shadow

Upon death, you spawn a strong-illusion that deals %illusion_outgoing_damage%% damage and takes %illusion_incoming_damage%% damage. Can cast all basic spells. Illusion casts %illusion_duration% seconds.

Name: Stormcrafter
Description:
Passive: Bottled Lightning

Zaps %max_targets% enemy targets within %range% range, dealing %damage% damage and a %slow%% slow for %slow_duration% seconds. Strikes every %interval% seconds.

Name: Overflowing Elixir
Description: Restores %health% health, and %mana% mana over %duration% seconds. Can capture runes.

Name: Ascetic's Cap
Description:
Passive: Endurance

Whenever a debuff would be applied to the owner, grant %status_resistance%% Status resistance and %slow_resistance%% Slow Resistance for %duration% seconds.

Name: Brigand's Blade
Description:
Passive: Dark Mercy

Your attacks deal %bonus_damage% more damage to enemies for each %missing_hp%% HP they are missing.

Name: Witchbane
Description:
Active: Cleanse

Dispel Target Enemy or Ally.

Dispel Type: Basic Dispel

Passive: Subjugate

Your attacks deal bonus damage equal to 4% of your target Max Mana.

Name: Pig Pole
Description:
Active: Pig, Out!

Turns your hero into a critter for %duration% seconds and gives them +%active_movespeed_pct%% Movement Speed.

Name: Tumbler's Toy
Description:
Active: Vault

Propels your hero forward %leap_distance% units. Tumbler's Toy gets disabled for 3 seconds if its owner receives damage from a player source.

Name: Fae Grenade
Description:
Active: Shadow Brand

Throws a Mark towards an enemy within %abilitycastrange% range applying a debuff that deals %dps% damage every second and provides vision of the unit for %duration% seconds.

Name: Seeds of Serenity
Description:
Active: Verdurous Dale

Target the ground with a %radius% radius. Provides +%aura_health_regen% health regeneration to all allied units while they are in the area of effect. Lasts %duration% seconds.

Name: Lance of Pursuit
Description:
Passive: Hound

Attacking from behind slows enemies by %slow_pct_melee%% (%slow_pct_ranged%% if Ranged) and deals %backstab_damage% more damage. Slow lasts %slow_duration% second(s).

Name: Occult Bracelet
Description:
Passive: Rites of Eloshar

Each time the wearer is attacked, they gain a stack of %mana_regen% mana regen, up to %stack_limit% stacks. Stacks last for %stack_duration% seconds.

Name: Ogre Seal Totem
Description:
Active: Ogre Seal Flop

Flop forward like an ogre seal %max_bounces% times, dealing %flop_damage% damage and slowing enemies in a %radius% radius by %slow%% for %slow_duration% second on each bounce. %leap_distance% bounce distance.

Name: Harpoon
Description:
Active: Draw Forth

When targeting an enemy, fire a harpoon at them, that pulls you and the target closer together, up to %pull_distance_pct%% of the distance between you and your target. If the caster is melee, the hero and target are always pulled to within melee distance of each other.

Passive: Echo Strike

Causes melee attacks to attack twice in quick succession. The double attacks apply a %movement_slow%% movement slow for %slow_duration% seconds on each strike. Echo Strike cooldown: %passive_cooldown%s

Name: Defiant Shell
Description:
Passive: Reciprocity

When attacked, the hero counter-attacks a target within their attack range. %counter_cooldown%s Cooldown.

Name: Specialist's Array
Description:
Passive: Crackshot

Ranged Only. The next attack fires projectiles that deal %proc_bonus_damage% bonus damage at %count% additional targets within attack range plus a %secondary_target_range_bonus% range bonus. Does not trigger attack modifiers.

Name: Dagger of Ristul
Description:
Active: Imbrue

Consume %health_sacrifice% health to temporarily gain %bonus_damage% damage. Lasts %duration% seconds.

Name: Beloved Memory
Description:
Active: Honor the Dead

Place this Offering on an Altar to honor the dead with a memory from those they left behind.

Name: Scrying Shovel
Description:
Active: Dig

Search the map for Offerings to the dead.

Name: Forebearer's Fortune
Description:
Active: Undying Promise

Signal to the spirits of the other realm your commitment to honoring them. If everyone in the battle makes an Undying Promise before the fight begins, the dead might be willing to listen.

Name: Mercy & Grace
Description:
Active: Dead Shot

Fires a ghostly bullet at an enemy unit or tree. When the bullet strikes it will deal %damage% damage and slow the target by %impact_slow_percent%% for %impact_slow_duration% seconds, then ricochet in the vector-targeted direction. The ricochet will damage all units that it passes through, stopping when it hits a hero. Heroes hit by the ricochet will be feared for %ricochet_fear_duration% seconds in the direction of the shot.

Name: Tier 1 Token
Description: Activate to redeem a Tier 1 Neutral Item. The resulting neutral item isn't shareable and a hero can only redeem a single token per tier.

Name: Tier 2 Token
Description: Activate to redeem a Tier 2 Neutral Item. The resulting neutral item isn't shareable and a hero can only redeem a single token per tier.

Name: Tier 3 Token
Description: Activate to redeem a Tier 3 Neutral Item. The resulting neutral item isn't shareable and a hero can only redeem a single token per tier.

Name: Tier 4 Token
Description: Activate to redeem a Tier 4 Neutral Item. The resulting neutral item isn't shareable and a hero can only redeem a single token per tier.

Name: Tier 5 Token
Description: Activate to redeem a Tier 5 Neutral Item. The resulting neutral item isn't shareable and a hero can only redeem a single token per tier.

Name: Vindicator's Axe
Description:
Passive: Vengeance

Provides %bonus_damage% damage if equipped hero is Silenced and %bonus_armor% armor if equipped hero is Stunned.

Name: Duelist Gloves
Description:
Passive: Boldness

Grants %bonus_attack_speed% attack speed as long as there are enemy heroes within %radius% units.

Name: Ancient Guardian
Description:
Passive: Ancient Power

Grants %extra_bonus_damage% extra bonus damage as long as the unit is within %radius% range of an ancient.

Name: Safety Bubble
Description:
Passive: Bubbled Up

Equipped Hero has a %shield% HP Barrier against enemy damage. Barrier fully regenerates after not receiving damage for %restore_time% seconds. Self-inflicted damage bypasses the barrier.

Name: Whisper of the Dread
Description:
Passive: Tunnel Vision

Equipped Hero has their daytime vision reduced by %vision_penalty%% but their Spell damage increased by %bonus_spell_damage%%.

Name: Nemesis Curse
Description:
Passive: Glass Cannon

Hero takes %debuff_self%% more damage from all sources.

Passive: Glassify

When attacking a hero, apply a debuff increasing the damage received by that hero by %debuff_enemy%% for %debuff_enemy_duration% seconds. Only one target can be affected by Glassify at the same time.

Name: Aviana's Feather
Description:
Passive: Free Bird

When equipped hero is below %flight_threshold%% HP, they gain flying movement.

Name: Unwavering Condition
Description:
Passive: Unwavering

Hero's Max Health is set to %max_health% and can't be altered by other effects or attributes.

Name: Horizon's Equilibrium
Description:
Passive: Equilibrium

Damage dealt to and received from units further than %distance% units from you is reduced by %damage_reduction%%.

Name: Blighted Spirit
Description:
Passive: Toxins

Whenever an enemy attacks you, they gain -%heal_reduction% Heal Amplify/Lifesteal amplification for 3 seconds.

Name: Dandelion Amulet
Description:
Passive: Magical Damage Block

Every %AbilityCooldown%s, blocks up to %magic_block% magic damage from damage instances over %min_damage% damage.

Name: Turtle Shell
Description:
Active: Turtle

Silences and Disarms your hero for %duration% seconds. Reduce all incoming damage by %damage_reduction%%. This effect is removed when your hero moves.

Name: Martyr's Plate
Description:
Active: Martyrdom

Redirect %damage_redirection%% of all magic damage dealt to your allied heroes within %aura_radius% radius towards you for %duration% seconds.

Name: Gossamer Cape
Description:
Passive: Sixth Sense

Automatically dodge an attack from an enemy hero.

Name: Light Collector
Description:
Active: Lightbreak

Produce a brilliant flash of light that destroys trees in a %tree_destruction_radius% AoE.

Passive: Unclouded

Provides wearer with health regeneration during the day and mana regeneration during the night. When within a %radius% distance of any trees, health and mana regeneration are decreased by %penalty%%.

Name: Rattlecage
Description:
Passive: Reverberate

After taking %damage_threshold% damage from any source, the wearer fires a projectile at up to %target_count% random enemies in a %radius% radius, prioritizing heroes, that deal %projectile_damage% physical damage and slow the targets movement and attack speed by %slow%% for %slow_duration%s.

Name: Doubloon
Description:
Toggle: Flip

Toggle to convert %conversion_pct%% of your Max Health to Max Mana, or %conversion_pct%% of your Max Mana to Max Health. Mana and health regeneration from Doubloon is increased by %regen_bonus_pct%%, based on the which side is selected.

Name: Roshan's Banner
Description:
Use: Place Banner

Creates a banner at the target location. Lane creeps in the area of effect become damage immune while the Banner is up. Lasts %duration% seconds.

Can be destroyed. Melee hero attacks deal 2x damage to the banner.

Name: Black Grimoire
Description:
Use: Profane Knowledge

Hero kills and assists empower the Black Grimoire, granting it charges. Right-click to consume and grant %xp_per_charge% experience per charge. Starts on cooldown.
This item cannot be dropped.

Name: Gris-Gris
Description: This item that cannot be dropped or placed in the backpack but can be put into normal inventory slots. When the owner dies, %death_gold_lost_reduction_pct%% of the gold lost from death is added to the item, and will be refunded when the item is consumed. Right-click to consume and permanently remove the item.
